<svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path classname="inner-triangle" d="M10 8L16 12L10 16V8Z" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg></div><span class="embedded-post-cta">现在听</span></div><div class="embedded-post-meta">15 天前 · 2 个赞 · 3 条评论 · 布拉德·德隆</div></div><p>Anyway, on to this week&#39;s list of interesting things.我今天有心情谈论国际事务。</p><h4> 1. India&#39;s amazing poverty reduction</h4><p>过去几年，人们一直在争论印度到底在多大程度上<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/herecomesindia">减少了贫困</a>。每个人都知道它减少了很多，但有些人声称真实的数字不如引人注目的头条新闻<a href="https://documents1.worldbank.org/curated/en/099249204052228866/pdf/IDU0333e60f901267045600be83093783b77e67a.pdf">那么令人印象深刻</a>。嗯，我们有一些新的数字，以及一些方法上的改进。你猜怎么着？ India&#39;s poverty reduction has been even <em>more</em> impressive than the headlines had suggested! Surjit Bhalla 和 Karan Bhasin<a href="https://www.brookings.edu/articles/india-eliminates-extreme-poverty/">透露了独家新闻</a>：</p><blockquote><p>印度刚刚发布了 2022-23 年官方<a href="https://www.mospi.gov.in/sites/default/files/publication_reports/Factsheet_HCES_2022-23.pdf">消费支出数据</a>，为印度提供了十多年来首次基于调查的官方贫困估计……印度[转向]更准确的修正混合回忆期 (MMRP)，该数据要求家庭消费者最近7天的易腐烂品（例如水果、蔬菜、鸡蛋）的支出，最近365天的耐用品以及最近30天的所有其他物品的支出……[此方法]是其他国家的标准……</p><p>高增长和不平等现象的大幅下降相结合，消除了印度的贫困，按购买力平价 1.9 美元计算的贫困线[以 2011 年美元计算]……按购买力平价 3.2 美元计算，[贫困]从 53.6% 下降到 20.8%……请注意these estimates do not take into account the free food (wheat and rice) supplied by the government to approximately two-thirds of the population, nor utilization of public health and education…</p><p>数据显示，印度的贫困人口数量在这两个阈值上都明显低于世界银行的估计数字。该机构依靠消费者金字塔家庭调查（一个私人提供的数据源）得出 2020 年贫困率分别为 10%（按 1.90 美元）和 45%（按 3.20 美元），尽管<a href="https://www.elibrary.imf.org/view/journals/001/2022/069/article-A001-en.xml">Bhalla、Bhasin</a>解释了该数据存在众所周知的问题<a href="https://www.elibrary.imf.org/view/journals/001/2022/069/article-A001-en.xml">和维尔玛尼 (2022)</a> …</p><h4><strong>贫困 HCR（2011 年购买力平价 1.9 美元）</strong> </h4><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fad65472b-1c85-4d45-b4f6-0b41b5081d82_1082x862.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fad65472b-1c85-4d45-b4f6-0b41b5081d82_1082x862.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fad65472b-1c85-4d45-b4f6-0b41b5081d82_1082x862.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fad65472b-1c85-4d45-b4f6-0b41b5081d82_1082x862.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fad65472b-1c85-4d45-b4f6-0b41b5081d82_1082x862.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fad65472b-1c85-4d45-b4f6-0b41b5081d82_1082x862.png" width="1082" height="862" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/ad65472b-1c85-4d45-b4f6-0b41b5081d82_1082x862.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:862,&quot;width&quot;:1082,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:null,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:null,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;: