itter-view&amp;utm_source=twitter&amp;utm_content=view&amp;sref=R8NfLgwS">泰勒·考恩</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>你可以看到过去两年令人担忧的扁平化。但那些年，加拿大的人口<em><a href="https://worldpopulationreview.com/countries/canada-population">持续增长！</a></em>所以人均生活水平正在下降！</p><p>泰勒还发布了加拿大收入中位数上升的图表。但他的图表结束于 2021 年——当前增长放缓开始之前！所以这也不太让人放心。</p><p>泰勒指出，实际人均 GDP 是使用 GDP 平减指数而不是消费者价格来根据通货膨胀进行调整的。他将我们链接到<a href="https://twitter.com/stephenfgordon/status/1764439558001721715">加拿大经济学家史蒂芬·戈登 (Stephen Gordon) 的帖子</a>，他认为加拿大在海外销售的商品价格不如加拿大人购买的商品价格重要，因此我们应该看看按消费价格缩减的实际人均 GDP索引代替。</p><p>然而，当戈登执行此计算时，结果看起来更令人担忧！加拿大扣除CPI后的实际人均GDP在过去两年绝对暴跌，现在仅比十年前高一点！ </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2f503150-b5a5-4012-848e-eae2fda660c6_1059x834.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2f503150-b5a5-4012-848e-eae2fda660c6_1059x834.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2f503150-b5a5-4012-848e-eae2fda660c6_1059x834.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2f503150-b5a5-4012-848e-eae2fda660c6_1059x834.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2f503150-b5a5-4012-848e-eae2fda660c6_1059x834.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto: